invalid type: string "6.md\n\n# Mullet (Flathead Grey Mullet) (*Mugil cephalus*)\n\n## 1. Taxonomy & Nomenclature\n\nScientific Name: *Mugil cephalus* (Linnaeus, 1758)[^1]\n\nFamily: Mugilidae (mullets)[^1]\n\nGlobal Common Names: Flathead grey mullet, striped mullet, black mullet, grey mullet, bully mullet, hardgut mullet.[^2][^3][^1]\n\nRegional & Local Names:\nrd Puffer, Green Pufferfish.1\n\nĸ